--- case 54 options gfm label-bytes 35 input-bytes 469 expected-bytes 1235
should match containers like GitHub
--- input
# Tables in things

## In lists

*   Unordered:

    | A | B |
    | - | - |
    | 1 | 2 |

1.  Ordered:

    | A | B |
    | - | - |
    | 1 | 2 |

*   Lazy?
    | A | B |
    | - | - |
   | 1 | 2 |
  | 3 | 4 |
 | 5 | 6 |
| 7 | 8 |

## In block quotes

> W/ space:
> | A | B |
> | - | - |
> | 1 | 2 |

>W/o space:
>| A | B |
>| - | - |
>| 1 | 2 |

> Lazy?
> | A | B |
> | - | - |
> | 1 | 2 |
>| 3 | 4 |
| 5 | 6 |

### List interrupting delimiters

